    "name": "section-hero",
    "content": "<!-- AI-IMAGE: hero-bg | Main homepage hero image. Wide, warm photo capturing the practice personality.\n       SEARCH KEYWORDS: dental clinic hero image, patient smiling, modern dental office wide shot, welcoming reception.\n       REQUIREMENTS: Landscape, minimum 1920x1080, professional quality, warm lighting.\n       FALLBACK: Any wide clinic/office interior photo or smiling patient photo.\n       INSTRUCTION: Replace ONLY the url() value inside the section's background-image style; keep the linear-gradient overlay intact. Do not render this as an <img> element. -->\n<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero relative w-full min-h-[600px] lg:min-h-[800px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-0 bg-gray-900 bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat text-ivory\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('https://picsum.photos/1920/1080?random=10');\">\n  <div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 text-center flex flex-col items-center\">\n    <!-- AI-CONTENT: hero-heading | Replace with scraped business tagline or hero heading.\n         Max 8 words. Keep warm, inspirational tone. Can use <br /> for line break.\n         Example: \"Love yourself,<br />love your smile.\" -->\n    <h1 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-heading font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 md:mb-8 font-medium\">\n      Love yourself,<br />love your smile.\n    </h1>\n    <!-- AI-CONTENT: hero-subtext | Replace with scraped business description or hero subtitle.\n         1-2 sentences. Mention core services and welcoming tone. -->\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-subtext text-gray-100 mb-8 md:mb-12 max-w-2xl text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl font-sans leading-relaxed\" opacity-90>\n      Comprehensive dental care for every member of your family, delivered with compassion and precision. Experience dentistry designed around your comfort and confidence.\n    </p>\n    <!-- AI-CONTENT: hero-cta | Replace button text and href with the business's primary call-to-action. -->\n\n    <!-- AI-CONTENT: cta-label | Choose label by business.category:\n       - Endodontist / Endodontics → \"Book Appointment\"\n       - Orthodontist / Orthodontics → \"Schedule a Consultation\"\n       - Default / other dental → \"Request a Consultation\"\n       Apply the same label consistently across header, body, and footer CTAs for this site. -->\n\n    <a href=\"/consultation\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-cta-button px-8 md:px-10 py-3 md:py-4 font-medium transition-all duration-200 flex items-center justify-center text-base md:text-lg bg-primary text-white shadow-lg hover:scale-105 w-full sm:w-auto rounded-full\">\n      Request a Consultation\n    </a>\n  </div>\n</section>"
  },
